snippet.title: Shark Attack for the Commodore VIC-20 / Commodore VC-20
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

???


Game description:

You were thrown from a pirate ship into shark-infested waters.
Now you have to trap the sharks and fill the entire screen to advance to the next level. The sharks, however, can bite through the nets, so be quick!

After every level 2 octopi join the fun. If you touch them you die!
